            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>In today's complex design environment, it is often overlooked that conducting a criticality analysis during the design stage is more vital than for a running unit. Many teams neglect to incorporate Reliability Centered Maintenance (RCM) practices during the initial phases of a project. It's important to note that RCM and criticality are not synonymous. The RCM standard (SAE JA1011) does not specifically address criticality as a key component.</p>
