        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>It is no surprise that during a telecom system outage, all hot work activities were halted until the system was fully restored. The significance of the HVAC system's role as a critical safety component was brought to my attention. The importance of these safety measures is evident in ensuring the overall safety of the work environment.</p>
